  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ChasisUUID
    Used to edit enable edit on child entities record alone

    Used to edit enable edit on child entities record alone
    EditDataWrapper
    Used to mark field used to store entity edited data
    EditEntity
    Used mark a field used to store edited entity name
    EditEntityId
    Used to mark field used to store edited entity id
    EntityName

    Used to mark a field to be filtered usually a @ManyToOne field

    ModifiableField

    Used to provide user friendly name to an entity
    Searchable

    TreeRoot
    Used to set the root of an entity
    Unique
    Used to identify unique fields
